data.description: Discover the charm of Rathdrum in this delightful 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home, perfectly positioned close to everything the town has to offer. This property boasts not only a prime location but also unique features that make it a rare find. Enjoy the tranquility of backing up to a neighborhood greenspace, offering privacy and stunning views of Rathdrum Mountain from your own fenced backyard. Practical amenities include RV parking and a handy storage shed. Whether you're an outdoor enthusiast or simply cherish peaceful living moments away from the convenience of town, this home is an ideal blend of comfort and accessibility.
